Meat and Potatoes: Simple Recipes that Sizzle and Sear
by Rahm Fama, Beth Dooley
English | ISBN: 0307985245 | 2014 | EPUB | 240 pages | 21 MB


Armed with a cast-iron skillet and the best ingredients he can find, meat-loving chef Rahm Fama serves up a fresh take on chuck wagon cuisine for flavorful meals you can enjoy no matter where you are.
Inspired by his early years on a Southwest cattle ranch, he followed his carnivorous curiosity across the country, seeking the choicest cuts and best ways to cook them. There's nothing like the thrill of throwing a pat of butter in a hot pan and searing a perfect steak, or grilling a pork chop, or braising chicken.
